### Hadith 3:192

*Narrated Ibn 'Abbas:*

The Prophet never fasted a full month except the month of Ramadan, and
he used to fast till one could say, "By Allah, he will never stop
fasting," and he would abandon fasting till one would say, "By Allah, he
will never fast."

